  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the most came to me when I was in the secret service.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew that people look after Eichmann.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was some people, they look after Eichmann, so it was look.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From 1950 that I was there till 1960, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I all the time knew that people look after him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and I didn't know what's the, what's the results, only when I was asked to join this mission.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was not ever, ever-- people make mistakes sometimes-- I will never knew about-- how do you say-- I'm not a-- how you call it-- Nazi hunter.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I just-- that was one of my operations for a month.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I work the Mossad 28 years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So people remember it, because it was a big, big, heroic act.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they justify it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But remember, other things are, you know, are not known, as it was now revealed only in these days, about two weeks ago, that I was the man who brought the scientists-- brought the names and the documents of the scientist who, after the war, want to kill again Israel through-- they want to build the missiles in Egypt.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was the man who, who revealed it and brought it, and brought it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How I was chosen?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So somebody had to be chosen then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Accidentally, it was me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would say it was the-- Ben-Gurion, the head of state, decided and gave the order to capture Eichmann from the beginning, or from the beginning, from '45, even was the head of the Jewish agency then.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And later, '48, he was the head of the Jewish state.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was an order stand all the time to capture Eichmann.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was in the secret service.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then because in 1960, I already was an operate of 10 years.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
